name: Turnaround photorealistic
description: This is an attempt to provide more suited pose files for turnaround pics generated through photorealistic checkpoints. Other options have very big margins which then generates characters with undetailed faces with photorealistic models.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description: A first version with only one pose. Both png and JSON are included. This is basically a pose taken from a picture, edited on GIMP to reduce the margins, then used to process a picture. The picture was then processed through the annotator.
